tool_description: An API to show GPS coords (Longitude, latitude),  Population,  Median Income and a lot more!
title: Australian Suburb Information

api_list.name: Filter by Postcode
api_list.description: Provides all suburb information based on the postcode entered
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://australian-suburb-information.p.rapidapi.com/postcode/{postcode}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "australian-suburb-information.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
